ZH: 我家的墙是白色的。
EN: The walls of my house are white.
ZH: 教室里的墙上挂满了学生的作品。
EN: The walls in the classroom are covered with students' artwork.
ZH: 这座城市的墙被涂成了五彩斑斓的颜色。
EN: The walls of this city are painted in all different colors.
ZH: 他们用砖头建造了一个高大的墙。
EN: They built a tall wall out of bricks.
ZH: 墙的外面是一个美丽的花园。
EN: Outside of the wall is a beautiful garden.
ZH: 这堵墙很厚，很难攀爬。
EN: This wall is very thick and difficult to climb.
ZH: 他画了一幅漂亮的壁画在这堵墙上。
EN: He painted a beautiful mural on this wall.
ZH: 这堵墙看起来很陈旧，需要重新装修。
EN: This wall looks very old and needs to be renovated.
ZH: 墙上有一道裂缝，需要尽快修补。
EN: There is a crack on the wall that needs to be fixed as soon as possible.
ZH: 她站在墙边观赏远处的景色。
EN: She stood by the wall and admired the view in the distance.
ZH: 这是一座历史悠久的城墙，已经有上千年的历史了。
EN: This is an ancient city wall that has a history of over a thousand years.
ZH: 墙壁上镶嵌着美丽的玻璃灯，灿烂夺目。
EN: The walls are ornamented with beautiful glass lamps, shining brightly.
ZH: 在中国，墙通常用中式砖块建造。
EN: In China, walls are often built with traditional Chinese bricks.
ZH: 墙上有一个小窗户，透过来阳光洒进房间。
EN: There is a small window on the wall, letting the sunlight into the room.
ZH: 这堵墙上涂满了各种各样的涂鸦。
EN: This wall is covered with all kinds of graffiti.
ZH: 他们在墙边生了一棵小树，让空地更加绿意盎然。
EN: They planted a small tree by the wall, making the area more lush.
ZH: 墙上的钟表指示着准确的时间。
EN: The clock on the wall shows the exact time.
ZH: 每逢节日，人们都会在墙上挂上灯笼。
EN: On every holiday, people hang lanterns on the walls.
ZH: 墙的外面是一条热闹的商业街。
EN: Outside of the wall is a bustling commercial street.
